**代码片段**:
```go
func (p *ResolvedPolicy) AllowedToolsCSV() string {
	return strings.Join(p.AllowedTools, ",")
}

func (p *ResolvedPolicy) Summary() string {
	parts := []string{fmt.Sprintf("permissions=%s", p.Permissions)}
	// ... 更多代码
	return strings.Join(parts, " ")
}

func SortedTools(tools []string) []string {
	out := append([]string(nil), tools...)
	sort.Strings(out)
	return out
}
```

**建议修复**:
添加测试用例验证这些函数的行为：
```go
func TestAllowedToolsCSV(t *testing.T) {
	policy := &ResolvedPolicy{AllowedTools: []string{"Read", "Write"}}
	if got := policy.AllowedToolsCSV(); got != "Read,Write" {
		t.Errorf("AllowedToolsCSV() = %q, want %q", got, "Read,Write")
	}
}

func TestSummary(t *testing.T) {
	policy := &ResolvedPolicy{
		Permissions:  "approve-all",
		PresetName:   "full-auto",
		AllowedTools: []string{"Read", "Write"},
	}
	summary := policy.Summary()
	if !strings.Contains(summary, "permissions=approve-all") {
		t.Errorf("Summary missing permissions: %s", summary)
	}
}
```

**原因**: 这些函数在代码中被使用（如 agent.go:522 调用 AllowedToolsCSV），但没有测试验证其正确性。

